{
  "video_id": "GMZVUtUhNwo",
  "title": "What's a Curator? | The Art Assignment | PBS Digital Studios",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 3090.0,
      "end_time": 5360.0,
      "text": "I want to come clean with\nyou guys about something."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5360.0,
      "end_time": 6790.0,
      "text": "Ever since \"The Art\nAssignment\" started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6790.0,
      "end_time": 8285.0,
      "text": "I've been calling\nmyself a curator."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 12620.0,
      "end_time": 14180.0,
      "text": "But it's a self given title."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14180.0,
      "end_time": 17040.0,
      "text": "When I worked at an art museum,\nI had that official title."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17040.0,
      "end_time": 19420.0,
      "text": "But now I'm taking a bit\nof liberty with the term."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19420.0,
      "end_time": 21710.0,
      "text": "So let's talk about\nwhat a curator actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21710.0,
      "end_time": 24630.0,
      "text": "is and whether or not I have\nany right to call myself one."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30300.0,
      "end_time": 33370.0,
      "text": "These days you hear the word\ncurator all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33370.0,
      "end_time": 34810.0,
      "text": "I curate my Tumblr."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34810.0,
      "end_time": 37220.0,
      "text": "He curates a collection\nof vintage sneakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37220.0,
      "end_time": 39710.0,
      "text": "She curated our music\nselection this evening."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39710.0,
      "end_time": 41210.0,
      "text": "And some people\nget their panties"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41210.0,
      "end_time": 43017.0,
      "text": "in a bunch over this\nuse of the term."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43017.0,
      "end_time": 44600.0,
      "text": "I don't really have\na problem with it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44600.0,
      "end_time": 45975.0,
      "text": "but I do want to\nthink about what"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45975.0,
      "end_time": 47370.0,
      "text": "it means in the\ntraditional sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47370.0,
      "end_time": 49000.0,
      "text": "and how the term\nmay have evolved."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 49000.0,
      "end_time": 52290.0,
      "text": "So the word curator comes\nfrom the Latin curo, curare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52290.0,
      "end_time": 55435.0,
      "text": "which for our application\nmeans to care for, to see to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 55435.0,
      "end_time": 56740.0,
      "text": "to worry about."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 56740.0,
      "end_time": 59310.0,
      "text": "So a curator is a person\nwho cares for something"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 59310.0,
      "end_time": 60800.0,
      "text": "or a collection of something."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 60800.0,
      "end_time": 62850.0,
      "text": "And you can care\nfor a lot of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 62850.0,
      "end_time": 66380.0,
      "text": "I used to care for contemporary\nart as a curator at a museum."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 66380.0,
      "end_time": 68110.0,
      "text": "And now I care for\ncontemporary art"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 68110.0,
      "end_time": 70010.0,
      "text": "as the producer\nbehind this show."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 70010.0,
      "end_time": 71520.0,
      "text": "But it's more\ncomplicated than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 71520.0,
      "end_time": 73750.0,
      "text": "Being a curator for a\ncollection-- whether it's"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 73750.0,
      "end_time": 76400.0,
      "text": "art, taxidermied\nanimals, rare coins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 76400.0,
      "end_time": 78220.0,
      "text": "widgets-- usually\nmeans you were hired"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 78220.0,
      "end_time": 80620.0,
      "text": "to care for that collection\nor part of the collection"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 80620.0,
      "end_time": 83767.0,
      "text": "by a museum or other institution\nthat owns those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 83767.0,
      "end_time": 86350.0,
      "text": "And you were are hired because\nyou have some special knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 86350.0,
      "end_time": 88160.0,
      "text": "or experience in that area."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 88160.0,
      "end_time": 90850.0,
      "text": "So you're either a specialist\nor on the road to becoming"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 90850.0,
      "end_time": 93350.0,
      "text": "a specialist, and there's\na reason why you're better"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 93350.0,
      "end_time": 95800.0,
      "text": "suited to steward the\ncollection than a random person"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 95800.0,
      "end_time": 96440.0,
      "text": "off the street."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 96440.0,
      "end_time": 98780.0,
      "text": "And you have to know that\ncollection in and out."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 98780.0,
      "end_time": 101080.0,
      "text": "You study it, you sort\nit, you write about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 101080.0,
      "end_time": 102990.0,
      "text": "you talk about it with\nother specialists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 102990.0,
      "end_time": 105480.0,
      "text": "and continually try to\nexpand your own education"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 105480.0,
      "end_time": 106500.0,
      "text": "on the subject."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 106500.0,
      "end_time": 108570.0,
      "text": "Figure out what needs\nconservation and think"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 108570.0,
      "end_time": 110660.0,
      "text": "about what's missing\nfrom the collection."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 110660.0,
      "end_time": 113250.0,
      "text": "Then you agitate and fund\nraise to fill the gaps"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 113250.0,
      "end_time": 115790.0,
      "text": "through acquisitions,\ncommissioning, exhibitions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 115790.0,
      "end_time": 116452.0,
      "text": "or programming."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 116452.0,
      "end_time": 118160.0,
      "text": "Then comes the part\nwhere you are arrange"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 118160.0,
      "end_time": 119460.0,
      "text": "the collection in rooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 119460.0,
      "end_time": 121370.0,
      "text": "OK, it's not really that simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 121370.0,
      "end_time": 123640.0,
      "text": "Let's call this step instead\npresenting the collection"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 123640.0,
      "end_time": 124400.0,
      "text": "to a public."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 124400.0,
      "end_time": 127020.0,
      "text": "This is done by making\nexhibitions, writing books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 127020.0,
      "end_time": 130810.0,
      "text": "essays, blog posts, labels,\ngiving tours and lectures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 130810.0,
      "end_time": 133300.0,
      "text": "training tour guides,\nwriting press releases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 133300.0,
      "end_time": 134370.0,
      "text": "and talking to the press."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 134370.0,
      "end_time": 136410.0,
      "text": "It's the curator's\njob to bridge the gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 136410.0,
      "end_time": 138140.0,
      "text": "between the material\nthey're presenting"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 138140.0,
      "end_time": 139870.0,
      "text": "and the people they're\npresenting it to."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 139870.0,
      "end_time": 141850.0,
      "text": "Some things are more\nself evident than others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 141850.0,
      "end_time": 143700.0,
      "text": "and it's the job of\nthe curator to provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 143700.0,
      "end_time": 145740.0,
      "text": "as much or as little\ninterpretation"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 145740.0,
      "end_time": 146661.0,
      "text": "as the material needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 146661.0,
      "end_time": 148410.0,
      "text": "When you're dealing\nwith contemporary art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 148410.0,
      "end_time": 150400.0,
      "text": "the curator's job\nis to best represent"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 150400.0,
      "end_time": 152420.0,
      "text": "that art and the\nartist who made it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 152420.0,
      "end_time": 154080.0,
      "text": "while also\nunderstanding the needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 154080.0,
      "end_time": 155370.0,
      "text": "and knowledge of the audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 155370.0,
      "end_time": 157740.0,
      "text": "Maybe the artist doesn't\nwant any explanation"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 157740.0,
      "end_time": 160760.0,
      "text": "of the artwork in the room with\nthe art, but you, the curator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 160760.0,
      "end_time": 162460.0,
      "text": "strongly believe\nyour audience needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 162460.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "some tiny morsel of information\nto effectively engage"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 166280.0,
      "text": "with the work."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 166280.0,
      "end_time": 168560.0,
      "text": "So you try to make the artist\nsee your point of view."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 168560.0,
      "end_time": 170720.0,
      "text": "And if that fails,\nyou make compromises"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 170720.0,
      "end_time": 173070.0,
      "text": "like posting information\nin a nearby gallery"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 173070.0,
      "end_time": 176250.0,
      "text": "or in a pamphlet or book\nor audio guide or online."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 176250.0,
      "end_time": 178400.0,
      "text": "Basically, you're the\nmiddleman or the midwife"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 178400.0,
      "end_time": 181310.0,
      "text": "or the mediator between the\nmaterial and the audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 181310.0,
      "end_time": 183050.0,
      "text": "You've got to try to\nknow your audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 183050.0,
      "end_time": 184156.0,
      "text": "and have empathy for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 184156.0,
      "end_time": 185530.0,
      "text": "You need to provide\nyour audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 185530.0,
      "end_time": 188330.0,
      "text": "with the tools they need to have\nthe best experience possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 188330.0,
      "end_time": 189290.0,
      "text": "with that material."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 189290.0,
      "end_time": 191010.0,
      "text": "But you have to weigh\nwhat's too little"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 191010.0,
      "end_time": 193900.0,
      "text": "and what's too much, what's\ntoo academic and art speaky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 193900.0,
      "end_time": 196116.0,
      "text": "and what's pandering,\nor overly simplified."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 196116.0,
      "end_time": 197740.0,
      "text": "And it's important\nto remember that you"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 197740.0,
      "end_time": 200240.0,
      "text": "can have a really diverse\naudience with vastly"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 200240.0,
      "end_time": 201090.0,
      "text": "different needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 201090.0,
      "end_time": 203024.0,
      "text": "It is the curator's\nobligation to try"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 203024.0,
      "end_time": 204440.0,
      "text": "to address those\nneeds responsibly"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 204440.0,
      "end_time": 206070.0,
      "text": "and to the best\nof their ability."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 206070.0,
      "end_time": 208170.0,
      "text": "Maybe you create labels\nor guides specifically"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 208170.0,
      "end_time": 210335.0,
      "text": "for kids, or an\naudio guide or tours"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 210335.0,
      "end_time": 211810.0,
      "text": "for those with special needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 211810.0,
      "end_time": 213820.0,
      "text": "OK, so what happens\nwhen you're a specialist"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 213820.0,
      "end_time": 215710.0,
      "text": "but you don't work\nfor an institution"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 215710.0,
      "end_time": 218320.0,
      "text": "and you don't have a given\ncollection to steward?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 218320.0,
      "end_time": 220150.0,
      "text": "You're an independent curator."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 220150.0,
      "end_time": 221850.0,
      "text": "And you initiate\nyour own projects"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 221850.0,
      "end_time": 224390.0,
      "text": "or are hired by others to\npresent material for them"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 224390.0,
      "end_time": 225990.0,
      "text": "on a temporary basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 225990.0,
      "end_time": 228125.0,
      "text": "And this is where the\nterm starts to loosen up."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 228125.0,
      "end_time": 230240.0,
      "text": "I am no longer\naffiliated with a museum"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 230240.0,
      "end_time": 232490.0,
      "text": "or a particular collection,\nso I'm technically"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 232490.0,
      "end_time": 234600.0,
      "text": "a specialist in\ncontemporary art and art"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 234600.0,
      "end_time": 238080.0,
      "text": "of the 20th and 21st century\nwho is applying that knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 238080.0,
      "end_time": 239210.0,
      "text": "to this new project."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 239210.0,
      "end_time": 241280.0,
      "text": "I'm still caring for\ncontemporary art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 241280.0,
      "end_time": 243330.0,
      "text": "and I'm doing that by\npresenting the artwork"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 243330.0,
      "end_time": 246630.0,
      "text": "and ideas of a wide range\nof artists working today."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 246630.0,
      "end_time": 249170.0,
      "text": "I'm commissioning artists to\ncreate assignments for you"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 249170.0,
      "end_time": 251126.0,
      "text": "and then I'm commissioning\nyou to make art"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 251126.0,
      "end_time": 252250.0,
      "text": "based on those assignments."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 252250.0,
      "end_time": 255730.0,
      "text": "Instead of a museum, I have the\nplatform of this video series."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 255730.0,
      "end_time": 257990.0,
      "text": "And I think about the\nseries holistically."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 257990.0,
      "end_time": 260200.0,
      "text": "I consider which artists\nto make episodes with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 260200.0,
      "end_time": 262250.0,
      "text": "in what order to\nshow them, how best"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 262250.0,
      "end_time": 264900.0,
      "text": "to introduce their work\nto you, what to ask them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 264900.0,
      "end_time": 267262.0,
      "text": "and how to contextualize the\nassignments historically."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 267262.0,
      "end_time": 269220.0,
      "text": "I try to think about what\nyou guys want to see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 269220.0,
      "end_time": 271250.0,
      "text": "or what you might not\nknow you want to see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 271250.0,
      "end_time": 273040.0,
      "text": "but that you'll like\nwhen you see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 273040.0,
      "end_time": 274540.0,
      "text": "I work with the\nartists we present"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 274540.0,
      "end_time": 276600.0,
      "text": "to think through assignments\nthat are feasible for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 276600.0,
      "end_time": 277475.0,
      "text": "but also challenging."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 277475.0,
      "end_time": 279916.0,
      "text": "If you're watching these videos\nand doing the assignments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 279916.0,
      "end_time": 281790.0,
      "text": "I'm hoping that you're\nbecoming more and more"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 281790.0,
      "end_time": 283984.0,
      "text": "familiar with the\nrecent history of art"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 283984.0,
      "end_time": 286400.0,
      "text": "and the ways of thinking that\nyou might be exposed to when"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
